In a multinational prospective registry, preoperative, intraoperative, perioperative and follow-up data on patients receiving thoracolumbar pedicle screw placement for degenerative disease or infections or tumors will be collected.

 The three arms consist of robot-guided (RG), navigated (NV), or freehand (FH) screw insertion.

